    {
      "id": "PopularPost216324",
      "post_content": "I always run 4 whenever I run [The Rack](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=The Rack) and [Wheel of Torture](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wheel of Torture) for maximum effect. However, I've found that in practice, this is the most fragile of the lot and it just doesn't stay on the field long enough to make up for the mana investment. Even worse, most creature removal (and [Disenchant](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disenchant)) is instant speed, so even if you run a lot of discard with the rax, they'll still have a chance to get rid of it. ",
      "posted_by": "Ideatog",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost216324\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I always run 4 whenever I run <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"The Rack\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=The Rack\">The Rack</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wheel of Torture\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wheel of Torture\">Wheel of Torture</a> for maximum effect. However, I've found that in practice, this is the most fragile of the lot and it just doesn't stay on the field long enough to make up for the mana investment. Even worse, most creature removal (and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Disenchant\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disenchant\">Disenchant</a>) is instant speed, so even if you run a lot of discard with the rax, they'll still have a chance to get rid of it. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '216324'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2063\">Ideatog</span>\r\n                                (12/15/2011 5:11:23 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRatin